This directory contains PHPUnit unit tests (www.phpunit.de) for the phpDays
package.

To run individual tests manually:

phpunit --include-path <path_to_your_local_phpdays'_svn_repos.> <test_file>

For example:

phpunit --include-path ~/svn/phpdays lib/Days/ViewTest.php

To run all tests available in a directory:

phpunit --include-path <path_to_your_local_phpdays'_svn_repos.> <directory>

Keep the bar green!
